Create "Gender" and "Year" Slicers 12

Step 1: Create Gender Slicer


1.     Double click on the Slicer Icon On the visualization bar.

2.     Slicer visual will display on the report.

3.     Drag and drop the “Sex” column from the DUI_Fatalities table

4.     Click on the drop-down button from the right corner of the header: Select “Between”

 

       Click on the Format icon on the visualization bar

a. Click General Tab:

·         Outline Color: Black

·         Out Put Weight: 1

·         X- Position: 877

·         Y Position:  0

·         Width: 200

·         Height: 104

·         Maintain Layer: Off

                              b. Slider Header: OFF

                              c. Title: ON

·         Title Text: Black

·         Type Title: Gender

·         Font: Black

·         Background: White

·         Alignment: Left

·         Text size: 17

·         Font family: DIN

   d. Background: On

·         Color: White

·         Transparency: 0

                            e. Border: ON

·         Color: White 10% Darker

·         Radius: 10


 

Follow the gif below to create a Gender Slicer 


Step 2:  Create Year Slicer 

1.      Double click on the Slicer Icon On the visualization bar.

2.      Slicer visual will display on the report.

3.      Drag and drop the “Year” column from the Calendar table

4.      Click on the drop-down button from the right corner of the header: Select “Between”

 

     Click on the Format icon on the visualization bar

a. Click General Tab:

·         Outline Color: Black

·         Out Put Weight: 1

·         X- Position: 1076

·         Y Position: 0

·         Width: 200

·         Height: 104

·         Maintain Layer: Off

                              b. Slider Header: OFF

                              c. Title: ON

·         Title: “Year”

·         Font: Black

·         Background: White

·         Alignment: Left

·         Text size: 17

·         Font family: DIN

   d. Background: On

·         Color: White

·         Transparency: 0

                            e. Border: ON

·         Color: White 10% Darker

·         Radius: 10



 Follow the gif below to create a Year Slicer
